# Fathom local API examples for editors with .http / REST Client support.
# Override the base URL if your backend runs on another port.
@base = http://127.0.0.1:8180
@model = echarlaix-tiny-random-phiforcausallm-model-safetensors

### Health
GET {{base}}/v1/health

### Install pinned tiny Phi SafeTensors fixture
POST {{base}}/api/models/catalog/install
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "repo_id": "echarlaix/tiny-random-PhiForCausalLM",
  "filename": "model.safetensors"
}

### List runnable OpenAI-style chat models
GET {{base}}/v1/models

### Non-streaming chat completion
POST {{base}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "{{model}}",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Say hello from a local Fathom API smoke test."
    }
  ],
  "max_tokens": 24
}
